div.div: The fourth season of Bungou Stray Dogs.

“LycoReco” is a café with a traditional Japanese twist located in downtown Tokyo. But the delicious coffee and sugary sweets are not the only orders this café takes! From delivering packages short distances, to pick-ups and drop-offs on the lonely streets at night, to zombies and giant monster extermination…?! Whatever your problem, we're here to help! We will solve any kind of "trouble" you may have!
Waiting for you are the ever-smiling poster-girl and the cool, serious newcomer. A petite girl who never wants to work and a young woman approaching thirty who wants to get married. And the manager is a nice guy who’s obsessed with Japan!
Whatever your order is, leave it all up to us♪
(Source: Official Site)
Tensei Shite Yandere Kouryaku Taishou Chara to Shujuu Kankei ni Natta Kekka

I was reborn as a Viscount's daughter, Cecil, in a very unexpected otome game where all of the love interests are Yanderes. However, Cecil, being the rival character in the game, was killed in every route by the chosen love interest. Furthermore, wishing to have a long life, Cecil meets Ashley who will be her servant and.... he's one of the Yandere love interests...!? (Source: Kadokawa, translated)
Totsuide kita Yome Aisouwarai Bakari Shiteru

A Samurai is worried about the fact that his wife always seems to wear a forced smile whenever she's with him. Note: initially self-published on the author's Twitter it later became serialized on Nico Nico Seiga where the story continued.
